# мӢӨм ң нҢҢмқј мғқм„ұ (dockerconfigjsonмқ„ л§Ңл“Өм–ҙ sopsлЎң лҙүмқё):
#   kubectl create secret docker-registry ghcr-pull \
#     --docker-server=ghcr.io --docker-username=sobok2026 \
#     --docker-password=<read:packages мҠӨмҪ”н”„ PAT> \
#     --dry-run=client --output=yaml \
#   | sops --filename-override kubernetes/apps/sobok/ghcr-pull/app/secret.sops.yaml \
#       --encrypt /dev/stdin > kubernetes/apps/sobok/ghcr-pull/app/secret.sops.yaml
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Secret
metadata:
  name: ghcr-pull
type: kubernetes.io/dockerconfigjson
data:
  .dockerconfigjson: <BASE64_DOCKERCONFIGJSON>
